---
title: Rainbow Carrot & Tomato-Baked Couscous with Basil Pesto & Parmesan
description: Bake up the rainbow with only one tray and a whole lot of flavour. The carrots are glowing and the pops of blistered cherry tomato in the couscous give this bowl a vibrant burst. Cool it down with basil pesto and there you have it, a flavourful dinner we can all get behind.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

